\s Yakob Lefia Esau
\p
\v 1 Yakob lɔ́pʋ ɔkpa ɔyɔ́ á, Bulu abɔpʋ akʋ beyéfia mʋ.
\v 2 Brɛ́á Yakob lowun amʋ́á ɔlɛblɩ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, Bulu opútu ɔwakpa gyí nfɩ́! " Mʋ́sʋ́ ɔlɛtɩ ɩnʋ Mahanaim, mʋ́ asɩ gyí, "Opútu ɔwakpa anyɔ."
\s Yakob Lɔ́pʋ Atɔ́kiehɛ́ Sɩsɩ Esau Pʋ́ lwii Mʋ Ɩkʋlʋn
\p
\v 3 Yakob lɔ́wa abi gyankpá ɔbɛ́ɛ, bʋyɔtʋ mʋ pío Esau ánɩ́ ɔbʋ Seir ɔsʋlʋ́ʋsʋ, Edom ɔmátɔ.
\v 4 Bʋbláa mʋ wíe Esau bɛɛ, "Fʋ́ osúmpʋ́ Yakob ɔbɛ́ɛ, "Nayétsiá Laban wa, fɛ́ ɔfɔ́ɔ bʋtʋ ndɛ.
\v 5 nanya nantswié, afrimu, akufa pʋ́ nkpabi; nawa abi mbɛ́ɛ, bʋbɛ́bláa mɩ́ wíe mɛ́nɩ nɩ́ owun mɩ́ á, ansɩ́ bégyí mʋ."
\v 6 Abi amʋ bɛsankɩ bá Yakob wa bɛ́bláa mʋ bɛɛ, "Anɩ lɔ́yɔtʋ fʋ́ pío Esau. Alakʋsʋ́ ɔba béfia fʋ mʋ́a ɔdom ánɩ́ bʋgyí ahá alafa ana."
\v 7 Ifú lɛ́hɩɛ kɩtá mʋ. Mʋ́sʋ́ oleyé mʋ aha á bʋbʋ mʋ wa, akufa, nantswié pʋ́ akpɔsɔ ɔbʋ wá aku anyɔtɔ.
\v 8 Ɔlɔbwɛ́ agywɩɩn ɔbɛ́ɛ, "Nɩ́ Esau ɔbá bɔ́tsʋ ikú kʋlɛ blɩ́ɩ ɔbɛ́ɛ, mɔ́kɔ́ amʋ́ a, ikú nyɔsɩ amʋ ɔbɛtalɩ́ srɩ́."
\v 9 Yakob lɔbɔ mpaɩ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, "Oó! Mɩ́ naɩn Abraham Bulu, mɩ́ sɩ́ Isak mʋ sɩ́ Bulu, fʋ́ lɛ́bláa mɩ́ fɛ́ɛ́ nsankí yɔ́ mɩ́ ɔmátɔ, anyinki yɔ́ mɩ́ abusuanfɔ wa, tsúfɛ́ fɛ́ kpa mɩ.
\v 10 Mmɛfatá há nwɛ á fáwun mɩ pʋ́ ɔnɔ́kwalɩá fawá há mɩ fʋ́ osumpʋ. Brɛ́á nɛnatɩ́ woyia oyi-yiahɛ pɛ́ ndɛ asa nfa ɔbʋn Yordan ánfɩ. Támɛ sei ánfɩ mʋ́a, nabwɛ́ ɔdom anyɔ.
\v 11 Nobwipa lɛ́ mɩ́ tsú mɩ́ pío Esau ɩbɩtɔ, tsúfɛ́ ndɛ mʋ ifú nya ánɩ́ ɔbɛbá bɔmɔ́ anɩ fɛ́ɛ́, nyebi ánfɩ amʋ́a amʋ́ ayin.
\v 12 Yɛ́ fɛ́blɩ́ tswɩ fɛ́ɛ́, fɛ́kpa mɩ́ togyítɔ ɩbɔwa alɛ́ há mɩ́, fɔbwɛ́ mɩ́ abi ana bómoni fɛ́ ɔpʋ ɔnɔ́ osublu ánɩ́ ɔháa mɛ́ɛtalɩ klá mʋ́.
